{"tid":1648942,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我建議搞一個「連登文化大革命」","createTime":"2019-10-12T12:19:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T08:30:36.000Z","uid":319380,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5f9993e6c8241b3f079a16c417fbb28f5c1744b0","tid":1648942,"uid":319380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:19:24.000Z","msg":"我相信大家都知而家連登充滿大量五毛、分化撚、失敗撚、割𥱊撚。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有冇遇過一d NET teacher? 佢哋教學嘅手法同說話技巧，同d local teacher係好唔同嘅。<br />\nD鬼老教書，好重視鼓勵，盡量避免打擊學生嘅自信心。就算學生有乜唔好，佢哋都會先讚，再俾建議，最後鼓勵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登實在太多負面post<br />\n我建議大家出post 或回應時，可以參考呢個模式 (可根據實際情況加減)<br />\n<br />\n1. 讚 (係咪都搵d野讚咗先)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 建議 (其實係插緊你，但要用建議方法)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 鼓勵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算真係好嬲，好想放負，可以用連登豬黎沖走一d負能量，等其他人不會太難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n遇到只會放負嘅人，我地可以鼓勵佢地俾多d具體嘅建議，少一d埋怨、指責<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望連登充滿正能量，不要跌入敵人分化嘅陷阱<br />\n咁我哋先可以繼續去打呢場硬仗!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\np.s. 呢場運動完咗後，我不介意大家繼續互罵、講粗口，因為呢個係連登特色~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeeaa99d5de24ff356e9ac07b84edce60f6ad877","tid":1648942,"uid":197813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:21:58.000Z","msg":"其實同意唔好一嚟就屌人老母先 除非好明顯係5毛 不過可唔可以唔同用文革個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好掛住以前連登啲假膠post 仲有啲好搞笑嘅潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有感情台班死毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8afa33086961ecd1fdb7b1030312d305b08c69ea","tid":1648942,"uid":835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:22:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c79f3963389a467aae0f0cc4a4382d79e6dd15c0","tid":1648942,"uid":835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:22:49.000Z","msg":"但唔好用文化大革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ee460ed13402a1fc617fa01b7dbb13ae373d60","tid":1648942,"uid":265917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:23:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>小妹發現facebook好少文宣流通 <br />\n我自己一個帶風向帶到好絕望</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要記住尼場革命唔係淨係屬於連登仔<br />\n<br />\n四五十歲既人多數淨係上fb 佢地多數只會認同大眾都吹奏緊既野<br />\n<br />\n而藍屍page係fb大行其道<br />\n正所謂「識睇一定睇comment」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>所以我地要多啲係唔同post下面貼文宣同出下風向post </strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"c2003b4abd17505ed50957ff409505495110d1a1","tid":1648942,"uid":282118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c79f3963389a467aae0f0cc4a4382d79e6dd15c0","tid":1648942,"uid":835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:22:49.000Z","msg":"但唔好用文化大革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:23:52.000Z","msg":"agree<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f76850c4094066b07a64dfa951e943154edec3d","tid":1648942,"uid":835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2003b4abd17505ed50957ff409